HEADWORD: Creaturize
<hw>Crea"tur*ize</hw> <pr>(-⟦imac⟧z)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make
like a creature; to degrade</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Degrade and <qex>creaturize</qex> that mundane soul.</q>
